lead_paragraph: Aime Jacquet, who guided France to their 1998 World Cup triumph on home soil, believes the host nation have what it takes to knock out world champions Germany in their Euro 2016 semi-final on Thursday.

headline.print_headline: Jacquet Believes New French Generation Can Upset Germans
